!!!! Commit (2026-04-15)

```
feat: render tiddler-link-label as inline wikitext
```

The `tiddler-link-label` attribute is now rendered as inline wikitext instead of plain text, enabling transclusions (e.g. `{{$:/core/images/link}}`), HTML entities (e.g. `&#x1f517;`), and other wikitext markup as the link label.  The plugin CSS now sizes SVG icons inside `.so-tiddler-link` to `1em` so transclusions of core icons fit neatly alongside the row text.  A new //Tiddler Link Label// demo illustrates both forms.

